data.text: Dogu mouli nei, hagaamuina Dimaadua!
Dogu mouli nei, hagaamuina Dimaadua, hudee de langahia dono dumaalia.
Mee gu haga madammaa ogu huaidu huogodoo,
Mee e haga dagaloaha au gi daha mo taalunga,
Mee e haga honu dogu mouli gi nia mee humalia
Dimaadua la tangada hai gabunga e hagamaamaa digau ala gu haga daamaha,
Mee gu haga modongoohia gi Moses ana hagamamaanadu,
Dimaadua le e dumaalia ge e aloho, ge hagalee hagawelewele ngoohia
Mee hagalee helekai hai baahi gi nia daangada i nia madagoaa huogodoo.
Mee hagalee hagaduadua gidaadou gii tau gi tadau mee hala ala ne hai,
Tamanaiee o dono aloho i digau ala e hagalabagau Ia,
Dana hai dela ne haga mogowaa tadau huaidu gi daha mo gidaadou,
Di hai o tamana dela e humalia gi ana dama,
Mee e iloo Ia nia mee ala ne hai ai gidaadou.
Gei gidaadou la nia daangada hua dangada,
gei di madangi ga ili di maa, gei di maa gu hagalee,
Gei di aloho o Dimaadua i digau ala e hagalabagau Ia,
o digau ala e daudali ana hagababa ge e haga gila aga gii donu ana haganoho.
Dimaadua la gu haga noho dono lohongo king i di langi.
Goodou hagaamuina Dimaadua,
Goodou hagaamuina Dimaadua,
Goodou hagaamuina Dimaadua,
